[
    {
        "text": "Humans once wielded formidable magical power.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.09577464788732394,
        "end_progress": 0.09577464788732394
    },
    {
        "text": "But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.09577464788732394,
        "end_progress": 0.09577464788732394
    },
    {
        "text": "When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.09577464788732394,
        "end_progress": 0.09577464788732394
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a story of the end of the world, and the beginning of the next.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 28.0,
        "start_progress": 0.09577464788732394,
        "end_progress": 0.12112676056338029
    },
    {
        "text": "John was the second generation to start to have noticeable powers.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 28.0,
        "end_time": 52.0,
        "start_progress": 0.12183098591549296,
        "end_progress": 0.14507042253521127
    },
    {
        "text": "It was almost something that he had taken for granted, as he did not know what it was like before to have none.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 52.0,
        "end_time": 69.0,
        "start_progress": 0.1454225352112676,
        "end_progress": 0.18450704225352113
    },
    {
        "text": "There were now classes in the little school to teach the children how to harness their Mana and use it, in the hopes that one day a generation would be strong enough to take back their home.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 69.0,
        "end_time": 107.0,
        "start_progress": 0.18485915492957747,
        "end_progress": 0.2517605633802817
    },
    {
        "text": "John was now in his final year of school, and was one of the stronger students.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 107.0,
        "end_time": 125.0,
        "start_progress": 0.252112676056338,
        "end_progress": 0.27992957746478875
    },
    {
        "text": "While he was stronger, he was still not considered unusual, as there had been far more impressive people he had learned about in his history class.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 125.0,
        "end_time": 167.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2806338028169014,
        "end_progress": 0.3323943661971831
    },
    {
        "text": "He didn't know that one day that was about to change and he could hold the key to restoring order on his earth.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 167.0,
        "end_time": 185.0,
        "start_progress": 0.33274647887323944,
        "end_progress": 0.37183098591549296
    },
    {
        "text": "He was a tall, well-built young man with short brown hair and a friendly face.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 185.0,
        "end_time": 199.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3721830985915493,
        "end_progress": 0.3996478873239437
    },
    {
        "text": "Nothing that spoke to the powers that were laying in wait inside him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 199.0,
        "end_time": 219.0,
        "start_progress": 0.40035211267605636,
        "end_progress": 0.42464788732394365
    },
    {
        "text": "It was during a practice exercise that he began to feel different.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 219.0,
        "end_time": 235.0,
        "start_progress": 0.425,
        "end_progress": 0.4482394366197183
    },
    {
        "text": "The goal was to either provide a shield around yourself, or blast away a fake alien that was in the fight room.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 235.0,
        "end_time": 265.0,
        "start_progress": 0.44859154929577466,
        "end_progress": 0.4876760563380282
    },
    {
        "text": "A good student could be fairly impressive at one, although no one was really that great.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 265.0,
        "end_time": 291.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4880281690140845,
        "end_progress": 0.5190140845070422
    },
    {
        "text": "The instructors hoped that with practice though, the children would be powerful enough when they grew up to serve the security force well.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 291.0,
        "end_time": 317.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5193661971830986,
        "end_progress": 0.5679577464788732
    },
    {
        "text": "Suddenly it was John's turn.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 317.0,
        "end_time": 324.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5683098591549296,
        "end_progress": 0.5785211267605633
    },
    {
        "text": "He felt a cold stillness take over his body that he had never felt before.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 324.0,
        "end_time": 335.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5788732394366197,
        "end_progress": 0.6049295774647887
    },
    {
        "text": "And then suddenly it exploded around him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 335.0,
        "end_time": 343.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6052816901408451,
        "end_progress": 0.6197183098591549
    },
    {
        "text": "The fake alien flew back against the wall with such force that it clattered to the ground in pieces.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 343.0,
        "end_time": 361.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6200704225352113,
        "end_progress": 0.655281690140845
    },
    {
        "text": "But not only that, there was now a distinctive blue shield around John.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 361.0,
        "end_time": 375.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6556338028169014,
        "end_progress": 0.6806338028169014
    },
    {
        "text": "He had done both.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 375.0,
        "end_time": 380.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6809859154929577,
        "end_progress": 0.6869718309859155
    },
    {
        "text": "The instructors were stunned.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 380.0,
        "end_time": 386.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4,
        "end_progress": 0.6975352112676056
    },
    {
        "text": "No one could speak.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 386.0,
        "end_time": 392.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6982394366197183,
        "end_progress": 0.7049295774647887
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally they told John to release his shield and shower and get ready for his next class.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 392.0,
        "end_time": 406.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7052816901408451,
        "end_progress": 0.7366197183098592
    },
    {
        "text": "By the time he went home and had dinner for his family, he had forgotten about his display, but the school had not.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 406.0,
        "end_time": 425.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7369718309859155,
        "end_progress": 0.7774647887323943
    },
    {
        "text": "There was a knock at the door and the headmaster and the head of security were ushered into the sitting room.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 425.0,
        "end_time": 442.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7778169014084507,
        "end_progress": 0.8161971830985916
    },
    {
        "text": "They conferred with John's parents for quite some time.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 442.0,
        "end_time": 451.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8165492957746479,
        "end_progress": 0.8359154929577465
    },
    {
        "text": "\"John, we have some good news for you,\" his father said.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 451.0,
        "end_time": 470.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6978873239436619,
        "end_progress": 0.8559859154929578
    },
    {
        "text": "\" You are going to be given an opportunity that most can only dream of.\"",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 470.0,
        "end_time": 490.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8566901408450704,
        "end_progress": 0.8827464788732394
    },
    {
        "text": "\"You are going to the capital\" There were tears in his father's eyes but pride in his voice.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 490.0,
        "end_time": 507.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8830985915492958,
        "end_progress": 0.9151408450704225
    },
    {
        "text": "And John knew that while it was called an opportunity, he was not being given a choice.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 507.0,
        "end_time": 524.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9154929577464789,
        "end_progress": 0.9461267605633803
    },
    {
        "text": "His life path had been decided for him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 524.0,
        "end_time": 530.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9464788732394366,
        "end_progress": 0.9602112676056338
    },
    {
        "text": "And while he was scared he was also excited.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 530.0,
        "end_time": 540.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9605633802816902,
        "end_progress": 0.976056338028169
    },
    {
        "text": "He packed his bags and wondered how he would ever sleep that night.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 540.0,
        "end_time": 559.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9764084507042253,
        "end_progress": 1.0
    }
]